OL,3,CSwansea's flagship M&S store set to
OL,4,Cclose after being deemed 'unviable'
OL,6,FSwansea's retail landscape has been
OL,7,Fdealt a major blow after Marks and
OL,8,FSpencer (M&S) confirmed it is to close
OL,9,Fits historic flagship store later this
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FThe retailer, which has had a presence
OL,13,Fin the city for more than 100 years,
OL,14,Ftold staff on Tuesday, 24 February,
OL,15,Fthat the site is no longer "viable"
OL,16,Fand is expected to shut its doors for
OL,17,Fthe last time later in 2026.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
