OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1772132672
OL,3,CSwansea's flagship M&S store set to
OL,4,Cclose after being deemed 'unviable'
OL,6,FAround 92 employees are now facing an
OL,7,Funcertain future. M&S has confirmed
OL,8,Fthat a consultation process is
OL,9,Funderway, with the company aiming to
OL,10,Foffer staff alternative roles at
OL,11,Fnearby stores where possible.
OL,13,FThe decision comes as part of a UK-
OL,14,Fwide "store rotation" programme.
OL,16,FRichard Owen, M&S regional manager,
OL,17,Fsaid that while the store had been a
OL,18,F"key part of the community," the
OL,19,Fbuilding itself required significant
OL,20,Finvestment that did not align with the
OL,21,Fcompany's long-term growth plans.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
