FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1772132672
OL,3,CSwansea's flagship M&S store set to
OL,4,Cclose after being deemed 'unviable'
OL,6,F"Customer shopping habits are
OL,7,Fchanging," Mr Owen said.
OL,8,F"Unfortunately, it is not viable to
OL,9,Fkeep the store open as the building
OL,10,Ffaces practical and operational
OL,11,Fissues. We must prioritise long-term
OL,12,Fgrowth decisions."
OL,14,FThe news has sparked concern over the
OL,15,Ffuture of Swansea's city centre, where
OL,16,FM&S has long served as a primary
OL,17,F"anchor" tenant, drawing thousands of
OL,18,Fshoppers to the Oxford Street
OL,19,Fthoroughfare every week.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
