PN,46804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1772132672
OL,3,CSwansea's flagship M&S store set to
OL,4,Cclose after being deemed 'unviable'
OL,6,FSwansea Council expressed "extreme
OL,7,Fdisappointment" at the announcement,
OL,8,Frevealing it had spent several years
OL,9,Fworking behind the scenes to prevent
OL,10,Fthe closure.
OL,12,FA council spokesperson said: "The news
OL,13,Ffrom M&S is extremely disappointing
OL,14,Ffor staff and shoppers. M&S confirmed
OL,15,Fthat the current building and location
OL,16,Fis no longer suitable for their
OL,17,Fbusiness model, which has already seen
OL,18,F90 historic locations close nationwide.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
