PN,46805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1772132672
OL,3,CSwansea's flagship M&S store set to
OL,4,Cclose after being deemed 'unviable'
OL,6,F"We will continue working in the
OL,7,Fcoming weeks and months to seek a new
OL,8,Fsite that meets their needs and keeps
OL,9,FM&S in the city."
OL,11,FDespite the closure, M&S has insisted
OL,12,Fthe move is not a reflection on
OL,13,FSwansea as a retail destination and
OL,14,Fconfirmed it is "actively looking" for
OL,15,Fa more modern, "full-line" location
OL,16,Fwithin the city.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
