OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1772132672
OL,3,CSwansea's flagship M&S store set to
OL,4,Cclose after being deemed 'unviable'
OL,6,FFor now, the exact closing date
OL,7,Fremains unconfirmed, but the shutters
OL,8,Fare expected to come down later this
OL,9,Fyear, marking the end of an era for
OL,10,Fone of Wales' most famous shopping
OL,11,Fstreets.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/6
